com.vmware.vapi.core

Class MethodDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.core.MethodDefinition

  • public class MethodDefinition
extends Object
    The MethodDefinition class contains detailed information about a vAPI method. This should contain all the information required to address a method in the vAPI runtime.
